{"tid":678070,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一隻小學嘅遊戲","createTime":"2018-05-25T17:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T13:30:27.000Z","uid":56111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d74a40d59b52f58cfdd8c61f5268cf2a3cf60106","tid":678070,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"當年好早翻學校（天主教），去玩係地下部電腦<br />\n有兩隻game想搵翻<br />\n一隻係火警逃生，畫面係幾3d <br />\n最記得係要斟幾次茶，然後去廁所攞毛巾<br />\n再去窗邊揚，就會見到消防員救你<br />\n另一隻係遊戲係裡面有好多小遊戲<br />\n有拔蘿蔔，急流木筏，跳木樁，仲有好似馬戲團果隻揈「遷秋」etc <br />\n有冇人玩過或者知佢地叫咩名？"},{"pid":"ca46301dbc36d450ac4ebeb29176fbd8fd120d12","tid":678070,"uid":159962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"係咪日本貓仔果隻？<br />\n叫kutar"},{"pid":"e74a1f6fea65580226d57f7833b03e680be34ca1","tid":678070,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca46301dbc36d450ac4ebeb29176fbd8fd120d12","tid":678070,"uid":159962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"係咪日本貓仔果隻？<br />\n叫kutar"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"係，thanksssssssss <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a385b37f588cd8e52d4b37e5ae45a13fb550db4b","tid":678070,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"推一推"}]}